data.description: Seller willing to give $5,000 towards updates. If you're looking for your own space in the heart of Des Moines, look no further! This property offers a .39 acre lot and so many perks. The generous living area is perfect for entertaining and gives lots of natural light. The spacious kitchen boasts ample cabinet and countertop space to meet all your storage and cooking needs. With 1,243 square feet finished upstairs and 2 additional non-conforming bedrooms in the basement, this home accommodates a growing family, guests, or any other needs you may have. Don't overlook the expansive garage to suit all of your dreams. The three-car detached garage provides ample storage or a perfect workspace for your tools. Additionally, there's an attached carport that offers another parking spot, making this residence ideal for car enthusiasts. The sizable fenced-in yard adds to the charm of this property, providing even more space for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this exceptional home before it's off the market!
